都知道佢以前好花<br />\n佢雖然成日話愛我<br />\n但係我真係信唔過佢 因為我覺得有啲人就係本性難移 <br />\n我自己都唔知可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔想失去一個愛嘅人 唯有平時呃下自己"},{"pid":"cdff75bff011acc005cf83c48bc56038daef7176","tid":1473290,"uid":101414,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T21:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aaa35688c1e5e66c801db9ccad0928c0480ec81","tid":1473290,"uid":307270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3e93592b81ff3f9672bb44cbd418cf85973522df","tid":1473290,"uid":306780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:21:24.000Z","msg":"雖然同另一半一齊咗一年都幾穩定 亦都feel到佢都幾愛我<br />\n但係因為我地未一齊之前既時候佢實在同我講得太多關於佢同佢ex發生過既野 例如扑野嗰啲...仲形容得幾仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以成日不自覺地諗起佢地一齊相處既畫面<br />\n搞到自己成日都好唔開心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又會不斷比較自己同佢嗰ex 好怕自己比唔上佢<br />\n到底點先唔會再咁諗 好想放過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T22:00:54.000Z","msg":"我都會咁諗，後尾好serious 地同佢講左，話好介意，之後佢就無再提個ex 了。 我估最重要系溝通啦"},{"pid":"80769df05954091ad95ac171243a00c5aabb690a","tid":1473290,"uid":240336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cdff75bff011acc005cf83c48bc56038daef7176","tid":1473290,"uid":101414,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T21:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:03:27.000Z","msg":"講多啲ex缺點 以前有咩頂唔順佢 &lt;講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n可能我老婆都知我同 d ex咩原因散同埋係死症，所以佢對我 d ex冇乜野，照俾我出去食飯飲野。"},{"pid":"b73ab4ca5fd3a7b82885b563010bc9a8554a211f","tid":1473290,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e93592b81ff3f9672bb44cbd418cf85973522df","tid":1473290,"uid":306780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:21:24.000Z","msg":"雖然同另一半一齊咗一年都幾穩定 亦都feel到佢都幾愛我<br />\n但係因